          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gov-blue text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-navy mb-1">In-Person Drop-Off</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Come to City Hall (60 N. Parke Street) and drop off your permits or plans in the <strong>City Hall lobby Dropbox</strong>. Available during business hours.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-5">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-gov-blue text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-base font-bold text-navy mb-1">Electronic Submission</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Submit permits or plans electronically to the Planning & Community Development department. Contact them for the current submission email address.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
